OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,FThe Chair of Age Concern Jersey says
OL,7,Fhe is "deeply concerned" about
OL,8,Fproposals to change the way healthcare
OL,9,Fis paid for across the island.
OL,11,FIt comes as the Health and Care
OL,12,FCommittee announced a series of new
OL,13,Ffunding initiatives.
OL,15,FThese include:
OL,17,FHealth and Care says it is necessary
OL,18,Fto introduce these changes and
OL,19,F"identify areas where we can make
OL,20,Fbetter use of available resources" to
OL,21,Faddress rapidly rising costs.
