OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,FThe department is predicted to spend
OL,7,F#381 million in 2026 - with next
OL,8,Fyear's budget allocating an additional
OL,9,F#12 million to preventative and
OL,10,Fdigital healthcare, on top of the
OL,11,Fannually-awarded #15.6 million deficit
OL,12,Ffunding.
OL,14,FHowever, the department still faces a
OL,15,Fforecasted deficit of around #18
OL,16,Fmillion this year.
