OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,FBut Age Concern Jersey says these
OL,7,Fchanges - particularly the Emergency
OL,8,FDepartment fee - could have
OL,9,F"unintended and potentially dire
OL,10,Fconsequences for older adults in our
OL,11,Fcommunity".
OL,13,FBen Shenton, Chair of the charity,
OL,14,Fsays he fears the fees could deter
OL,15,Folder people from seeking necessary
OL,16,Fmedical attention - particularly if
OL,17,Fthey struggle to determine whether or
OL,18,Fnot their condition qualifies as an
OL,19,Femergency.
