OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,F"Our members have expressed worry that
OL,7,Fperhaps they won't go to A&E when they
OL,8,Fshould be going, because the rash is
OL,9,Fmore serious than they think it is, or
OL,10,Fthe headache, or the indigestion, or
OL,11,Fwhatever," he says.
OL,13,F"I don't think you should put
OL,14,Ffinancial barriers in the way of
OL,15,Fpeople seeking medical treatment,
OL,16,Fwhich is what this does."
