OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,FAge Concern Jersey is pushing for the
OL,7,Fintroduction of clear exemptions from
OL,8,Fthese fines or subsidies for older
OL,9,Fadults - particularly those on fixed
OL,10,For low incomes.
OL,12,FThe charity also wants an education
OL,13,Fcampaign to help residents understand
OL,14,Fwhen A&E visits are appropriate and
OL,15,Fwhat alternative services might be
OL,16,Favailable.
