OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,F"The single person old age pension in
OL,7,FJersey is around #270 per week", Mr
OL,8,FShenton adds, "so a #77 charge is
OL,9,Fquite a significant cost to some of
OL,10,Fthem just to go off and make sure that
OL,11,Fthe pains that they have are not
OL,12,Fsomething serious.
OL,14,F"What you don't want is someone not
OL,15,Fturning up who the following day then
OL,16,Fsuffers a fatality or catastrophe
OL,17,Fbecause they didn't want to pay to go
OL,18,Fand get checked out."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
