OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,F"I think some people will look more
OL,7,Fcritically and say, 'I can take this
OL,8,Fto my GP'," he explains. "So it should
OL,9,Ftake a bit of pressure off.
OL,11,F"And the good part about that is that
OL,12,Fsomeone who has potentially serious
OL,13,Fconditions like sepsis will go much
OL,14,Fmore quickly through the system - it's
OL,15,Fa case of prioritisation."
OL,17,FSo whilst the changes are not designed
OL,18,Fto discourage all patients from
OL,19,Fattending the Emergency Department,
OL,20,Fthey are designed to discourage some.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
