OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F388A1758718007
OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,F"What we're trying to avoid is a
OL,7,Fsituation like the one that was
OL,8,Fpointed out to me the other day where
OL,9,Fa child with a grazed arm turned up to
OL,10,FA&E," Deputy Binet says. "That really
OL,11,Fshould have gone to a GP."
OL,13,FThe Minister is also clear that the
OL,14,Fproposed new framework - the
OL,15,FTreatments and Interventions
OL,16,FPrioritisation Policy (TIPP) - will
OL,17,Fnot result in the "removal of any
OL,18,Fessential services".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
