OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,FWhilst he admits some patients may
OL,7,Fhave to pay for medicines they
OL,8,Fcurrently get for free, the TIPP is
OL,9,Fabout providing a clear set of
OL,10,Fguidelines about what the department
OL,11,Fpublicly funds, rather than cutting
OL,12,Ffunding for any critical treatment
OL,13,Fpathways.
OL,15,F"I don't think anybody needs to worry
OL,16,Fabout anything," Deputy Binet
OL,17,Fstresses. "This is a modernisation
OL,18,Fprocess, it's about formalising things
OL,19,Fthat go on informally. This is a way
OL,20,Fof organising the process of review."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
