OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,FThe framework gives the Minister
OL,7,Fhimself the final power to decide
OL,8,Fwhich treatments will continue to be
OL,9,Fpublicly funded.
OL,11,FHis decisions will be informed by
OL,12,Frecommendations from a team of
OL,13,Fprofessionals - including the island's
OL,14,FDirector of Public Health, the Chief
OL,15,FPharmacist, a GP representative, and
OL,16,Fthe Health Department's Finance
OL,17,FDirector.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
