OL,3,CA&E charges risk people avoiding vital
OL,4,Cmedical services, says charity
OL,6,FTheir recommendations will be reviewed
OL,7,Fby an advisory board, and an appeals
OL,8,Fprocedure will enable islanders to
OL,9,Fchallenge decisions.
OL,11,F"There's a long process of very
OL,12,Fprofessional people before it gets to
OL,13,Fthe lay people who make political
OL,14,Fdecisions," Deputy Binet explains.
OL,16,F"It's a very comprehensive process and
OL,17,Fone that I think should give people
OL,18,Fmore confidence in the health system."
